trans-unit.source: This topic lists the steps to build and deploy the <token>af_integration</token> solution.
trans-unit.target: This topic lists the steps to build and deploy the <token>af_integration</token> solution.

trans-unit.source: To build and deploy the solution
trans-unit.target: To build and deploy the solution

trans-unit.source: In <token>vsprvs</token>, right click the <embeddedLabel>FTP_EAI_Tutorial</embeddedLabel> solution, and then select <embeddedLabel>Build Solution</embeddedLabel>.
trans-unit.target: In <token>vsprvs</token>, right click the <embeddedLabel>FTP_EAI_Tutorial</embeddedLabel> solution, and then select <embeddedLabel>Build Solution</embeddedLabel>.

trans-unit.source: Once the build succeeds, right click the <embeddedLabel>FTP_EAI_Tutorial</embeddedLabel> solution, and then select <embeddedLabel>Deploy Solution</embeddedLabel>.
trans-unit.target: Once the build succeeds, right click the <embeddedLabel>FTP_EAI_Tutorial</embeddedLabel> solution, and then select <embeddedLabel>Deploy Solution</embeddedLabel>.

trans-unit.source: In the deployment window, the <embeddedLabel>Deployment Endpoint</embeddedLabel> is a read only entity, and this value is reflected from the <embeddedLabel>BizTalk Service URL/Namespace</embeddedLabel> set in the itinerary designer.
trans-unit.target: In the deployment window, the <embeddedLabel>Deployment Endpoint</embeddedLabel> is a read only entity, and this value is reflected from the <embeddedLabel>BizTalk Service URL/Namespace</embeddedLabel> set in the itinerary designer.

trans-unit.source: Enter the Access Control namespace for <token>af_integration</token>, Issuer Name, and Shared Secret.
trans-unit.target: Enter the Access Control namespace for <token>af_integration</token>, Issuer Name, and Shared Secret.

trans-unit.source: The <token>vsprvs</token> Output pane displays the deployment progress and result.
trans-unit.target: The <token>vsprvs</token> Output pane displays the deployment progress and result.

trans-unit.source: The URL where the bridge is deployed is also displayed in the Output pane.
trans-unit.target: The URL where the bridge is deployed is also displayed in the Output pane.
